Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:31.88,Logo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(700,1600)\move(365,55,360,95,0,5028)}{\t(0,5445,\fs63)}Queen's Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen's Blade.{Oro: isn't this the same as OVA 01? Some phrases are different in this one.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a tournament held once every four years to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the queen who would rule over the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new queen abolished the nobility and brought equality to the commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cities flourished, and civilization progressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.59,0:00:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people enjoyed their newfound prosperity under the new regime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this also marked the beginning of a ruthless rule under an iron fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:36.22,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\fscy105\be1\fad(600,0)\pos(358,314)}A sister's agony – The door of faith opens once more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus begins the prelude to the battle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between the beautiful warriors who fight for their beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really hits the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're holding your liquor well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:01:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bring more ale and meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Lord, thank you for the food tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, God is so lame! He never does anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We even tried that praying crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what? Worshipping Satan might not be a bad idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,especially if it makes me stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tolerate such blasphemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You trying to pick a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see that we're enjoying our drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna make it up to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease this immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'll have to brand you as heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be judged guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and burned at the stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a load of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks she's an inquisitor or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's obviously still in training!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That does it! You're going to regret that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making a racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me eat my dinner in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! She was in the last Queen's Blade tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Steel Princess Ymir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she's really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen her in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so small too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, who said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Steel Princess Ymir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did somebody say she wants to become stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, the fastest way is to buy my fine weapons from Steel Mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the beauties, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you buy one now, you'll get another one for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Buy my weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it on my tab!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Siggy of the 19th Holy Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our meeting must be part of God's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're certainly one rash sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not wise to start trouble with that unruly lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my duty to admonish those who speak ill of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a fundamentalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me. You were going to use holy powers, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that always happens when I panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything even with God's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they would all die in a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the seeds of heresy should not be allowed to take root.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To overlook them is to betray those who have placed their trust in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about some weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owning a weapon from Steel Mountain might give you an edge in your missionary work{\fscx168.815944}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God hath decreed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Those who believe in me shall be blessed with love and happiness."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Those who worship demons shall be granted mercy and purified with fire."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pray to me. Believe in me."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Faith is the only way to salvation."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, it looks like I've run into a nutcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of God is for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please shower me with your hot, passionate blessings!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clouds have cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll make it to Gainos by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you also headed for Gainos?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've received orders from the Holy See to pray at the cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning to sell these weapons from Steel Mountain to Claudette.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Claudette is an esteemed figure who favors the church
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has given greater authority to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These weapons shall someday be used
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to hack those demon worshippers into bloody chunks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, perhaps. It really depends{\fscx168.815944}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ymir, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's destroy the heretics together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This child is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coms! Coms! {Komusu? wtf - Cums (Oro)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has gone to the village to look for a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he might not make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us borrow the power of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be right as rain soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save this boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. God's power is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, God's power is nothing compared to your...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you couldn't use your holy power last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you managed to do it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I kept my calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I get flustered, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's hard not to panic with a sword pointed at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power is needed as well to punish the heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do so, I've learned some martial arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's quite impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd thought we'd be able to reach Gainos before the day ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to aim to reach there before dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but mountain paths are creepy at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel dispirited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is always with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if God is with us, snakes will still appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be enjoying yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this torch, I can set afire any heretics that may cross our path!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that mountain bandits appear around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some traveler probably got attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking a righteous follower of God is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ymir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I don't want to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, if those travelers had Steel Mountain weapons with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they wouldn't need to be afraid of bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take the torch with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snakes will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave your possessions and get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I cut you in half?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease this at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A servant of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbecoming to gang up on a frail old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, there are so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lot! I have some good news for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even bandits such as you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should have heard of the fine weapons from Steel Mountain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to{\fscx168.815944}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish. I haven't even gotten to the good part yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let them have a taste of my Steel Mountain weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ymir, I shall fight as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to teach the insolent fools a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shut your whore mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your first time, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight without a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, wanna buy some?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Give me a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want an axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a shield as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that! Give me a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget my shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These bandits are rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't made such a killing in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did the right thing giving her that weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword isn't like the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice expression you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't belittle God's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May the Lord be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight you next!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having trouble with one sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're their leader, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pray to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beg for his forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God will forgive even a brigand such as you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you vow to turn over a new leaf and serve God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you wouldn't look down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you people of the church,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't put food on the table with faith alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not submit, I'll take you as heretics!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heretics?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, all of us feel more at home with Satan than God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked heretics, just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remorse...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd planned to spare your life if you'd just give up your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm no longer in the mood for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God does not abandon his believers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Perhaps this will change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you plan to fight so many at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, pray to your god.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you're dead. I hope you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect nothing less of the woman who rules over the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that sword won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd do well to buy one of the finest weapons of Steel Mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the one used by Reina, the winner of the previous Queen's Blade tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, the Evindil Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The sword of the Wandering Warrior Leina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When dealing the final blow,\Nyou have to use a sword like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or else you won't look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's going to cost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just sell it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've helped you to stall for time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you said your last prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who believe in God\Ncannot possibly be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Then die as you pray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Place your trust in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't fall like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Gainos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you really lack mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you torched all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they were heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Purifying them with fire is another display of God's affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, time to part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun traveling with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Stay well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The money for the weapon I gave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want money for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Steel Princess Ymir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have made up your mind, Siggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the name of our Lord and the Holy See,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby decree you an inquisitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I order you as an inquisitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn every heretic, pagan, and disobedient follower!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will!{? so many kanji for "in"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will the Goddess of Victory cast her smile upon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will blaze a path to achieve her heart's desires?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until they cross swords, only God knows.
